            <h2>Meet Jayla</h2>
            <h4>Born July 2000</h4>
            <p>Jayla is a talkative young woman. She is friendly and outgoing.</p>
<p>She wants to grow up and become a fashion designer one day, but she’ll settle for going to school and getting good grades for now. She’s most proud of getting As and Bs, and she likes to hang out in the library or go shopping during her free time.</p>
<p>She likes to listen to a lot of different music, but R&B, jazz, gospel, and rap are her favorites. She loves to hear Nicki Minaj on the radio. Jayla also likes <i>Disney Channel</i> cartoons and <i>Disney</i> movies.</p>
<p>She hopes to someday go to Disneyland or Disney World.</p>
<p>Jayla needs a family thatcan teach her to cope with her emotions and encourage her to continue being a bright and wonderful young woman.</p>

